{"id":260,"date":"2025-08-29T12:28:29","date_gmt":"2025-08-29T06:58:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp\/?page_id=260"},"modified":"2025-08-31T02:56:31","modified_gmt":"2025-08-30T21:26:31","slug":"video-gallery","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/video-gallery\/","title":{"rendered":"Video Gallery"},"content":{"rendered":"        <section class=\"ispl-hero-wrap\" style=\"background: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Benefits_Doing-Good-Feels-Good-scaled.jpg');background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(13,34,64,0.9) 0, rgba(13,34,64,0.1) 100%), url('https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Benefits_Doing-Good-Feels-Good-scaled.jpg'); \">\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-overlay\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);\"><\/div>\r\n            <div class=\"ispl-hero-inner\" style=\"position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:6rem 1.25rem;\">\r\n                                    <h2 style=\"font-size:3rem; line-height:1.1; margin:0 0 1rem;\">Stories of Service in Motion<\/h2>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"font-size:1.125rem; max-width:800px;\">\u201cSome moments cannot be captured by words alone\u2014they must be seen, heard, and felt. The Video Gallery of the Lions Club of Balasore brings to life the spirit of our service, showcasing the stories, emotions, and transformations that define our mission. Each video is more than just moving images; it is a living testimony of compassion in action, of communities uplifted, and of lives forever changed. From heartfelt projects and service campaigns to celebrations of unity and leadership, these visual stories connect hearts across boundaries and inspire others to join the cause. Through these films, we invite you to witness how ordinary acts of kindness, when united under the banner of Lions, create extraordinary change.\u201d<\/p>\r\n                                                    <p style=\"margin-top:2rem;\">\r\n                        <a href=\"https:\/\/lionsclubbls.org\/our-projects\/\" class=\"ispl-hero-btn\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.9rem 1.5rem; background:#ffcc00; color:#111; text-decoration:none; border-radius:.35rem; font-weight:600;\">\r\n                            Our Projects                        <\/a>\r\n                    <\/p>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n        <\/section>\r\n        \n<div class=\"yt-grid-gallery\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:20px;\"><div class=\"yt-video-block\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/dIAXWLbnaro\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><h6 style=\"margin-top:5px;text-align:center;font-size:14px;\">WHAT IS LIONS CLUB | LIONS CLUB INTERNATIONAL KYA HAI | LION CLUB MEMBERSHIP | LIONS INTERNATIONAL<\/h6><\/div><div class=\"yt-video-block\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/Q_xlrWVy4mg\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><h6 style=\"margin-top:5px;text-align:center;font-size:14px;\">LIONS CLUB \u0915\u094d\u092f\u094b\u0902 JOIN \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902 | BENEFITS OF JOINING LIONS CLUB | LIONS CLUB KI MEMBERSHIP KYON LEN<\/h6><\/div><div class=\"yt-video-block\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/6nah4OHTjqE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><h6 style=\"margin-top:5px;text-align:center;font-size:14px;\">LIONS CLUB INTERNATIONAL FEE STRUCTURE | LIONS CLUB ME KITNA FEES HOTA HAI  LIONS CLUB MEMBERSHIP<\/h6><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed